            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of steel smelting reduction equipment, and relates to an iron ore powder reduction device and method.The iron ore powder reduction device is characterized in that an upper-section reduction bin, a middle-section transition bin, a lower-section reduction bin and an air inlet bin are sequentially connected and communicated in a sealed mode, and the upper-section reduction bin and the lower-section reduction bin are connected through a material conveying pipe; according to the invention, a gas inlet system is utilized to provide reducing gas with sensible heat, and the reducing gas is sequentially used as a heat source for solid-solid reduction reaction, a heat source for gas-solid reduction reaction and fluidized reducing gas, so that the purpose of directly reducing iron ore powder by simultaneously utilizing the reducing gas and a solid reducing agent is achieved. The iron ore does not need to be sintered, and hydrogen and/or coal gas and coal can be directly used for reducing the iron ore powder, so that energy consumption and carbon emission are reduced in the whole process, the requirements for the gas amount, temperature and quality of reducing gas are reduced, and the method is suitable for the development process of pure hydrogen smelting. And the iron ore is reduced in the transition stage with the limited hydrogen production capacity."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于钢铁冶炼还原设备技术领域，涉及一种铁矿粉还原装置和方法，将上段还原仓、中段过渡仓、下段还原仓和进气仓依次相互连接并且相互之间密封联通，并将上段还原仓、下段还原仓通过物料输送管相连，形成相互连通的密闭的还原环境，利用进气系统提供带有显热的还原气体，依次作为固固还原反应的热源和气固还原反应的热源和流化还原气体，达到了同时利用还原气和固态还原剂直接对铁矿粉进行还原的目的。由于无需对铁矿进行烧结，并且能够直接利用氢气和/或煤气、煤炭进行铁矿粉的还原，因此从整个流程上减少了能源消耗和碳排放，降低了对还原气体气量、温度和品质的要求，适用于向纯氢冶炼发展过程中，氢气产能受限的过渡阶段对铁矿的还原。"
                }
            ]
